  "special": {
    "title": "Flee the Wave, Dude!",
    "description": "Fires 13 slow horizontal projectiles in a wave-like pattern. The shots pierce targets and can ricochet several times off surfaces, while keeping the usual Jakobs shotgun critical-hit bonus."
  },
  "notes": "It originally appeared as a Loot Hunt drop from DJ Tanner, and a later hotfix boosted both its damage and its ricochet behavior. In cramped spaces the bouncing pellets can easily down the user. Maya can exploit the multi-hit pattern for strong Life Tap healing and quick reload pacing, while Gaige benefits heavily because missed shots and ricochets can still redirect into enemies and hit repeatedly in enclosed rooms.",
